                      </svg>
                      DCF算出ロジックの数学的定義 (Technical Methodology)
                    </span>
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 transform group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
