                            <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?%5Cdpi%7B150%7D%20%5Cbg%7Bwhite%7D%20PV_%7BFCF%7D%20%3D%20%5Csum_%7Bt%3D1%7D%5E%7B10%7D%20%5Cfrac%7BFCF_t%7D%7B%281%2BWACC%29%5Et%7D" alt="FCF PV" class="dark:invert h-10" />
                          </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-4 pt-6 border-t border-skin-line/30 text-left">
                          <p class="text-skin-accent font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">■ 継続価値 (Terminal Value)</p>
                          <div class="flex justify-center py-3">
                            <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?%5Cdpi%7B150%7D%20%5Cbg%7Bwhite%7D%20TV%20%3D%20%5Cfrac%7BFCF_%7B10%7D%20%281%2BR_f%29%7D%7BWACC%20-%20R_f%7D" alt="Terminal Value" class="dark:invert h-12" />
                          </div>
                          <p class="opacity-60 text-[10px] font-sans text-center border-t border-skin-line/10 pt-2">11年目以降を永遠に成長を仮定（成長率 = R_f）</p>
                        </div>

                        <div class="space-y-4 pt-6 border-t border-skin-line/30 text-left">
                          <p class="text-skin-accent font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">■ 企業価値 (Enterprise Value)</p>
                          <div class="flex justify-center py-3">
                            <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?%5Cdpi%7B150%7D%20%5Cbg%7Bwhite%7D%20EV%20%3D%20PV_%7BFCF%7D%20%2B%20%5Cfrac%7BTV%7D%7B%281%2BWACC%29%5E%7B10%7D%7D" alt="EV" class="dark:invert h-10" />
                          </div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                    <div>
                      <h4 class="font-bold text-skin-accent mb-4 border-l-4 border-skin-accent pl-2">4. 理論株価 (Fair Price) 算出</h4>
                      <p class="text-sm mb-4">企業価値から有利子負債を差引き、現金を加算後、発行済株式数で除します。</p>

                      <div class="bg-skin-fill/20 p-6 rounded-md space-y-4 overflow-x-auto text-center font-serif">
                        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
                          <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?%5Cdpi%7B150%7D%20%5Cbg%7Bwhite%7D%20EquityValue%20%3D%20EV%20%2B%20Cash%20-%20Debt" alt="Equity Value" class="dark:invert h-8" />
                          <img src="https://latex.codecogs.com/svg.latex?%5Cdpi%7B150%7D%20%5Cbg%7Bwhite%7D%20FairPrice%20%3D%20%5Cfrac%7BEquityValue%7D%7BSharesOutstanding%7D" alt="Fair Price" class="dark:invert h-12" />
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>

                  </div>
                </details>
              </div>

              <div class="p-4 bg-skin-fill/10 border border-skin-line rounded-lg text-xs leading-relaxed opacity-80">
                <p class="font-bold mb-2 flex items-center gap-1 text-skin-accent">
                  <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
                  </svg>
                  詳細なDCF分析モデルについて
                </p>
                <p>
                  このDCFモデルは、DefeatBeta APIのExcelテンプレートと同じロジックを用いて計算されています。
                  <strong>割引率 (WACC)</strong> は、キャップM（CAPM）モデルに基づき、銘柄独自のベータ値と市場のリスクプレミアムから算出されています。
                  <strong>成長率</strong> は過去3年間の実績（CAGR）を重み付けして予測のベースとしています。
                  <strong>※重要：</strong> DCF法による理論株価は、将来のキャッシュフロー予測という「仮定」に強く依存します。成長率が1%変化するだけで理論株価は数十パーセント変動する場合があるため、投資判断の際の「目安」の一つとしてご活用ください。
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ) : (
            <div class="p-8 bg-skin-fill/10 border border-skin-line rounded-lg text-center italic text-gray-500">
              この銘柄のDCF分析データは現在利用できません（金融セクターや指標不足など）。
            </div>
          )}
        </section>

        <hr class="my-12 border-skin-line" />

        <section id="analyst-ratings" class="mt-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6 border-b pb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-skin-accent" aria-hidden="true">target</span>
            {symbol}のアナリスト評価 (直近)
          </h2>
          {analystSummary ? (
            <div class="space-y-8">
              {/* Consolidated Summary & Target Price Block */}
              <div class="bg-skin-fill/20 p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg border border-skin-line shadow-sm">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12 divide-y lg:divide-y-0 lg:divide-x divide-skin-line/50">
                  
                  {/* Left Column: Target Price */}
                  <div class="pb-8 lg:pb-0 lg:pr-12">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-skin-accent" aria-hidden="true">target</span> 目標株価 (Target Price)
                    </h3>
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                      <div class="flex justify-between items-end border-b border-skin-line/30 pb-4">
                        <div>
                          <div class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-1">平均目標株価</div>
                          <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-skin-accent">{typeof analystSummary.targetMean === 'number' ? `$${analystSummary.targetMean.toFixed(2)}` : '---'}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-right">
                          <div class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-1">現在価格</div>
                          <div class="text-xl font-bold opacity-80">{typeof analystSummary.currentPrice === 'number' ? `$${analystSummary.currentPrice.toFixed(2)}` : '---'}</div>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                      
                      {typeof analystSummary.currentPrice === 'number' && typeof analystSummary.targetMean === 'number' && (
                        <div class="bg-skin-fill/20 px-4 py-3 rounded-md flex justify-between items-center">
                          <span class="text-sm font-medium">現在価格からの乖離</span>
                          <span class={`text-xl font-bold ${analystSummary.targetMean > analystSummary.currentPrice ? 'text-green-600' : 'text-red-600'}`}>
                            {analystSummary.targetMean > analystSummary.currentPrice ? '+' : ''}{((analystSummary.targetMean / analystSummary.currentPrice - 1) * 100).toFixed(1)}%
                            <span class="text-xs ml-1">{analystSummary.targetMean > analystSummary.currentPrice ? '上昇余地' : '下落予想'}</span>
                          </span>
                        </div>
                      )}
                      
                      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-center">
                        <div class="bg-skin-fill/30 p-3 rounded-md">
                          <div class="text-xs opacity-70 mb-1">最高</div>
                          <div class="text-lg font-bold text-green-600">{typeof analystSummary.targetHigh === 'number' ? `$${analystSummary.targetHigh.toFixed(2)}` : '---'}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="bg-skin-fill/30 p-3 rounded-md">
                          <div class="text-xs opacity-70 mb-1">最低</div>
                          <div class="text-lg font-bold text-red-600">{typeof analystSummary.targetLow === 'number' ? `$${analystSummary.targetLow.toFixed(2)}` : '---'}</div>
                        </div>
                      </div>

                      <div class="flex justify-between text-sm opacity-60 px-1 pt-2">
                        <span>アナリスト予想数: {analystSummary.opinions || '---'}人</span>
                        <span>中央値: {typeof analystSummary.targetMedian === 'number' ? `$${analystSummary.targetMedian.toFixed(2)}` : '---'}</span>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>

                  {/* Right Column: Overall Rating & Distribution */}
                  <div class="pt-8 lg:pt-0 lg:pl-12">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-6 flex items-center gap-2">
                      <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-skin-accent" aria-hidden="true">align_horizontal_left</span>
                      総合評価と推奨分布
                    </h3>
                    <div class="space-y-6">
                      <div class="flex justify-between items-center border-b border-skin-line/30 pb-4">
                        <div>
                          <div class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-1">総合評価</div>
                          <div class={`text-2xl font-bold ${analystSummary.assessmentColor}`}>{analystSummary.assessment}</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-right">
                          <div class="text-sm opacity-70 mb-1">平均スコア</div>
                          <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-skin-base">{typeof analystSummary.score === 'number' ? analystSummary.score.toFixed(2) : '---'} <span class="text-xs font-normal opacity-50">/ 5.0</span></div>
                        </div>
                      </div>

                      <div class="space-y-3">
                        {[
                          { label: "強気買い", key: "strongBuy", color: "bg-green-600" },
                          { label: "買い", key: "buy", color: "bg-green-400" },
                          { label: "中立", key: "hold", color: "bg-gray-400" },
                          { label: "売り", key: "sell", color: "bg-red-400" },
                          { label: "強い売り", key: "strongSell", color: "bg-red-600" }
                        ].map((rating) => (
                          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                            <span class="text-xs w-16 shrink-0 opacity-80">{rating.label}</span>
                            <div class="flex-grow h-2 bg-skin-fill/50 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                               <div 
                                 class={`h-full ${rating.color}`} 
                                 style={`width: ${analystSummary.total > 0 ? (analystSummary.ratings[rating.key] || 0) / analystSummary.total * 100 : 0}%`}
                               ></div>
                            </div>
                            <span class="text-xs font-medium w-6 text-right">{analystSummary.ratings[rating.key] || 0}</span>
                          </div>
                        ))}
                      </div>
                      <div class="text-right text-xs opacity-60">
                        推奨アナリスト合計: {analystSummary.total}人
                      </div>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>

              {/* Recent Analyst Rating Changes */}
              {reportData.rating_changes && reportData.rating_changes.length > 0 && (
                <div class="mt-12 overflow-x-auto bg-skin-fill/10 p-4 rounded-lg border border-skin-line">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4 px-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-skin-accent" aria-hidden="true">note_stack</span> 最近のレーティング変更
                  </h3>
                  <table class="min-w-full divide-y divide-skin-line text-sm">
                    <thead class="bg-skin-fill/20">
                      <tr>
                        <th scope="col" class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">日付</th>
                        <th scope="col" class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">調査会社</th>
                        <th scope="col" class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">格付け</th>
                        <th scope="col" class="px-4 py-3 text-left font-semibold">アクション</th>
                        <th scope="col" class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold">変更時株価</th>
                        <th scope="col" class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold">目標株価 (旧→新)</th>
                        <th scope="col" class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold">変更時比</th>
                        <th scope="col" class="px-4 py-3 text-right font-semibold text-skin-accent bg-skin-fill/5">現在比</th>
                      </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody class="divide-y divide-skin-line">
                      {reportData.rating_changes.map((change: any) => {
                        const currentPrice = reportData.analyst_ratings?.currentPrice;
                        const basePrice = change.PriceAtRating;
                        const targetPrice = change.currentPriceTarget;
                        const upsideAtRating = (basePrice > 0 && targetPrice > 0) ? (targetPrice / basePrice - 1) * 100 : null;
                        const upsideCurrent = (currentPrice > 0 && targetPrice > 0) ? (targetPrice / currentPrice - 1) * 100 : null;
                        
                        return (
                        <tr class="hover:bg-skin-fill/10">
                          <td class="px-4 py-3 whitespace-nowrap opacity-80">{change.GradeDate}</td>
                          <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium">{change.Firm}</td>
                          <td class="px-4 py-3">
                            <span class={`font-bold ${
                              change.ToGrade?.toLowerCase().includes('buy') || change.ToGrade?.toLowerCase().includes('outperform') || change.ToGrade?.toLowerCase().includes('overweight') 
                              ? 'text-green-600' : 
                              change.ToGrade?.toLowerCase().includes('sell') || change.ToGrade?.toLowerCase().includes('underperform') || change.ToGrade?.toLowerCase().includes('underweight')
                              ? 'text-red-600' : 'text-skin-base opacity-70'
                            }`}>
                              {translateGrade(change.ToGrade)}
                            </span>
                          </td>
                          <td class="px-4 py-3 italic opacity-70">
                            {(() => {
                              const action = change.Action?.toLowerCase();
                              let text = change.Action || '---';
                              let colorClass = '';
                              
                              if (action === 'up') {
                                text = `格上げ (up)`;
                                colorClass = 'text-green-600 font-semibold not-italic';
                              } else if (action === 'down') {
                                text = `格下げ (down)`;
                                colorClass = 'text-red-600 font-semibold not-italic';
                              } else if (action === 'main') {
                                text = `維持 (main)`;
                              } else if (action === 'reit') {
                                text = `再確認 (reit)`;
                              } else if (action === 'init') {
                                text = `新規開始 (init)`;
                              }
                              
                              return <span class={colorClass}>{text}</span>;
                            })()}
                          </td>
                          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right whitespace-nowrap opacity-70">
                            {change.PriceAtRating ? `$${change.PriceAtRating.toFixed(2)}` : '---'}
                          </td>
                          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right whitespace-nowrap">
                            <div class="flex items-center justify-end gap-1.5">
                              {change.priorPriceTarget > 0 && (
                                <span class="text-xs opacity-50">${change.priorPriceTarget}</span>
                              )}
                              {change.priorPriceTarget > 0 && change.currentPriceTarget > 0 && (
                                <span class="text-xs opacity-30">→</span>
                              )}
                              {change.currentPriceTarget > 0 ? (
                                <span class={`font-bold ${
                                  change.priorPriceTarget > 0
                                  ? (change.currentPriceTarget > change.priorPriceTarget ? 'text-green-600' : change.priorPriceTarget > change.currentPriceTarget ? 'text-red-600' : '')
                                  : ''
                                }`}>
                                  ${change.currentPriceTarget}
                                </span>
                              ) : (
                                !(change.priorPriceTarget > 0) ? (
                                  <span class="opacity-30">---</span>
                                ) : null
                              )}
                            </div>
                          </td>
                          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right whitespace-nowrap">
                            {upsideAtRating !== null ? (
                              <div class="flex flex-col items-end">
                                <span class={`font-bold ${upsideAtRating > 0 ? 'text-green-600' : upsideAtRating < 0 ? 'text-red-600' : ''}`}>
                                  {upsideAtRating > 0 ? '+' : ''}{upsideAtRating.toFixed(1)}%
                                </span>
                              </div>
                            ) : (
                              <span class="opacity-30">---</span>
                            )}
                          </td>
                          <td class="px-4 py-3 text-right whitespace-nowrap bg-skin-fill/5">
                            {upsideCurrent !== null ? (
                              <span class={`font-bold ${upsideCurrent > 0 ? 'text-green-600' : upsideCurrent < 0 ? 'text-red-600' : ''}`}>
                                {upsideCurrent > 0 ? '+' : ''}{upsideCurrent.toFixed(1)}%
                              </span>
                            ) : (
                              <span class="opacity-30">---</span>
                            )}
                          </td>
                        </tr>
                      )})}
                    </tbody>
                  </table>
                </div>
              )}

              <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-8">
                ※平均スコアは 1.0(強気買い)から5.0(強い売り)の範囲で算出しています。<br />
                ※アナリストの推奨評価の合計人数を表示しています。投資の最終判断はご自身で行ってください。
              </p>
            </div>
          ) : (
            <p class="text-gray-500">アナリスト評価データは現在利用できません。</p>
          )}
        </section>

        <JapanBrokers reportData={reportData} />

        <!-- トップに戻るボタン -->
        <div class="mt-12 mb-20 text-center">
          <a href="#" class="px-6 py-2 bg-skin-card border border-skin-line rounded-full text-sm font-bold hover:text-skin-accent hover:border-skin-accent transition-all inline-flex items-center gap-2">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-4 w-4" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M14.707 12.707a1 1 0 01-1.414 0L10 9.414l-3.293 3.293a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414l4-4a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
            ページトップへ戻る
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    )}
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

